text: Submarine Command is a 1951 American war movie directed by John Farrow and William Holden, Nancy Olson, William Bendix, Don Taylor, Arthur Franz, Daryl Hickman, Peggy Webber, Jerry Paris. It was distributed by Paramount Pictures and was a box office failure. ==References== ==Other websites== * * * Category:1951 war movies Category:American war movies Category:World War II movies Category:Movies set underwater Category:Paramount Pictures movies Category:Movies directed by John Farrow Category:Movies set in California
